nodes.text: The Prince of Waves was a tourist liner that operated sometime prior to around the year 3643 BBY. It made its centennial voyage around the planet Manaan, but sunk during the journey and came to rest on the edge of an ocean trench. In around 3643 BBY scavengers searched the cruiser's untouched wreck for salvage.
The Prince of Waves was first mentioned as part of the scavenging crew skills mission "Rust and Riches" in the 2011 BioWare MMORPG Star Wars: The Old Republic.
